Cyberpunk style: A lone hacker's workstation in a neon-drenched room, featuring a worn mechanical keyboard with glowing cyan keys, multiple holographic terminal screens floating in mid-air displaying cascading streams of XML code and API data flows. The screens cast electric blue and magenta reflections on a cluttered desk covered with scattered microchips and tangled fiber optic cables. Rain streaks down a grimy window in the background, revealing a dystopian cityscape of towering server farms with blinking lights. A steaming cup of synthetic coffee sits forgotten beside the keyboard, wisps of vapor catching the neon glow. The atmosphere is moody and focused, capturing the solitary joy of a developer automating tasks in the dead of night.
